\begin{figure}
\includegraphics[scale=0.7]{figure7-eps-converted-to.png}
\caption{Rate of energy dissipation per unit volume, $\phi$, during the impact process on: (a) a smooth solid surface ($r_f$ = 1) and (b) a rough solid surface ($r_f$ = 1.2), at different time instances ($t \in$ [0.5 ms, 1.5 ms]).
